CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 21, reads: "5. Miss Virginia Davis, winner of the Artcraft Mantel Company mantel clock"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of man presenting Virginia Davis with mantel clock from Artcraft Mantel Company, standing in front of demonstration kitchen including Jessie Vann, in the Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
